# Addition

Axiom.  There is a binary operation + : ‚Ñï ‚Üí ‚Ñï ‚Üí ‚Ñï such that for all x, y ‚àà ‚Ñï,

  a. x + 0 = x.
  b. x + s(y) = s(x + y).

Lemma.  For all x, y ‚àà ‚Ñï, x + (y + 0) = (x + y) + 0.

Theorem (associativity of addition).  For all x, y, z ‚àà ‚Ñï,

    x + (y + z) = (x + y) + z.

Lemma.

    a. For all x ‚àà ‚Ñï, 0 + x = x.
    b. For all x, y ‚àà ‚Ñï, s(x) + y = s(x + y).

